        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Unvented cylinder. The Formby multi-bathroom standard.</strong><p>Fed directly from the mains, delivering hot water at mains pressure simultaneously to every bathroom in the property. The right choice for Formby 4 and 5 bedroom properties, loft conversion projects and any property adding an en suite. G3 qualified installation required by law. Supply and fit from £900.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Immersion heater replacement. Quick restoration of hot water.</strong><p>When the cylinder is in good condition but the element has failed. Element replacement from £150 typically restores hot water on the same visit. We confirm whether the cylinder is in adequate condition to justify the element replacement or whether full replacement is the more economical approach.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Indirect cylinder. Heated by boiler with immersion backup.</strong><p>The most common type in Formby homes with system or regular boilers. Heated via a heat exchanger coil from the central heating boiler. Available in both vented and unvented configurations depending on the property's pressure requirements.</p></div></div>
